# OrderFlow — Local Deployment Contract

> Cloud targets are N/A (D-14). Everything runs via `docker compose up`. This locks the
> service list, ports, and env contract; the actual `docker-compose.yml` + Dockerfiles are
> built in M1 (infra + services) and extended each milestone.

## Containers & ports (host)
| Service | Port | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| postgres | 5432 | one instance, 4 schemas, per-service user (D-04) |
| kafka (KRaft) | 9092 | single broker, no Zookeeper (D-05) |
| redis | 6379 | idempotency keys + saga locks |
| order-service | 8080 | REST + SSE + orchestrator + outbox relay |
| inventory-service | 8081 | M1 |
| payment-service | 8082 | M2 |
| shipment-service | 8083 | M3 |
| zipkin | 9411 | tracing (M4) |
| prometheus | 9090 | metrics scrape (M4) |
| grafana | 3000 | dashboards (M4) |
| frontend | 5173 (dev) / 8088 (served) | React dashboard (M4) |

## Compose phasing
- **M1:** postgres + kafka + redis + order-service + inventory-service.
- **M2:** + payment-service.
- **M3:** + shipment-service.
- **M4:** + zipkin + prometheus + grafana + frontend.
- Healthchecks on infra; services `depends_on` infra healthy. Named volumes for PG/Kafka data
  (git-ignored: `pgdata/`, `kafka-data/`).

## Dockerfile strategy
- Each Java service: multi-stage (Maven build → slim JRE 21 runtime, e.g. `eclipse-temurin:21-jre`).
- Frontend: build with Node → serve static via nginx (or Vite dev in dev compose).
- One parent build; per-module image.

## Env contract (`.env.example` — names only, no values)
```
# Postgres
POSTGRES_HOST, POSTGRES_PORT, POSTGRES_DB
ORDER_DB_USER, ORDER_DB_PASSWORD
INVENTORY_DB_USER, INVENTORY_DB_PASSWORD
PAYMENT_DB_USER, PAYMENT_DB_PASSWORD
SHIPMENT_DB_USER, SHIPMENT_DB_PASSWORD
# Kafka
KAFKA_BOOTSTRAP_SERVERS
# Redis
REDIS_HOST, REDIS_PORT
# Observability (M4)
OTEL_EXPORTER_ZIPKIN_ENDPOINT
# Service ports (optional overrides)
ORDER_PORT, INVENTORY_PORT, PAYMENT_PORT, SHIPMENT_PORT
```
- Secrets never committed; `.env` git-ignored; only `.env.example` in repo.
- Spring config via env-var overrides of `application.yml` (12-factor).

## Build/test gate before run
- `mvn verify` (units + TestContainers integration) green before `docker compose up`.
